No. 22,

Misc.

Peak v. United States. John S. Wrinkle for petitioner. Simon E. Sobeloff, then Solicitor General, Assistant Attorney General Doub, Samuel D. Slade and Alan S. Rosenthal for the United States.

Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Sixth Circuit granted.
